claim.claim-text:
1. A semiconductor device comprising:
a gate electrode over a substrate;
a gate insulating film over the gate electrode;
a semiconductor film over the gate insulating film; and
a source electrode and a drain electrode over the semiconductor film,
wherein the gate electrode includes gallium and zinc.

6. A semiconductor device comprising:
a gate electrode over a substrate;
a gate insulating film over the gate electrode;
a semiconductor film over the gate insulating film; and
a source electrode and a drain electrode over the semiconductor film,
wherein the gate electrode includes indium and zinc.
